DEFINITIONS

"Software" refers to FDK (Faded Dream Kit), including all source code,
binaries, assets, themes, icons, documentation, and associated files in
this repository, in whole or in part, modified or unmodified.

"Author" refers to FemBoyGamerTechGuy, the original creator and sole copyright
holder of the Software, and any successor publicly designated by the Author
in writing.

"You" / "User" refers to any individual or entity other than the Author
accessing, using, copying, modifying, or distributing the Software.

"Personal Use" means use solely by a single natural person for their own
private, non-commercial purposes on their own devices. It does not include
use by or on behalf of any company, organisation, group, or legal entity.

"Commercial Use" means any use intended for or resulting in commercial
advantage, monetary compensation, or business benefit of any kind.

"Fork" means any copy, clone, or derivative of the Software's repository or
source code, stored locally, hosted privately, or published publicly.

"Redistribution" means sharing, publishing, packaging, uploading, or otherwise
making the Software or any derivative available to any third party in any form.

"Permission Grant" means a written authorisation issued by the Author to a
specific individual or entity permitting otherwise-restricted actions. Every
Permission Grant is personal, non-transferable, and subject to the conditions
stated within it and within this license.

"Dependent Project" means any software project that links against, embeds,
or otherwise uses FDK as a library component, whether at compile time or
runtime.

