FDK (Faded Dream Kit) is the sole, exclusive, and absolute property of the
Author. No individual, entity, corporation, contributor, or user of the
Software holds any ownership, co-ownership, shared rights, or equity of any
kind over FDK or any part of it. Nothing in this license, the sublicense/
directory, or any Permission Grant creates, implies, or transfers any
ownership interest in FDK to any party other than the Author.

As the sole copyright holder, the Author retains full, perpetual, and
unrestricted rights over the Software, including but not limited to:

  a) Using the Software for any purpose without restriction.

  b) Selling, licensing, sublicensing, or monetising the Software or any
     derivative in any form, including closed-source or private builds.

  c) Making any version of the Software private, restricted, or paid at
     any time and without notice.

  d) Changing the license of future versions at any time.

  e) Issuing, modifying, or revoking Permission Grants at any time, for
     any reason or no reason, with or without notice. Upon revocation all
     rights granted to that party immediately and permanently cease.

  f) Mandating at any time that any Fork or Dependent Project be made
     open source, made private, taken down, or altered in any way the
     Author specifies, regardless of prior compliance. The party must
     comply within the timeframe specified, or immediately if none is given.

  g) Transferring copyright and all associated rights to a designated
     successor, who then holds all Author rights under this license in full.

Nothing in this license restricts the Author's own use of the Software.
All restrictions apply only to other users.

