  c) The Fork must not be relicensed.
  d) Visibility (public or private) is determined solely by the Author.
     Forks are private by default unless the Author states otherwise.
  e) The Author may request takedown, privatisation, or deletion of any
     Fork at any time, for any reason, without prior notice. The Fork
     owner must comply immediately.

